    dc:creator "Klompen, H." ;
    dc:date "2010" ;
    dc:title "Holothyrids And Ticks: New Insights From Larval Morphology And Dna Sequencing, With The Description Of A New Species Of Diplothyrus (Parasitiformes: Neothyridae)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5392494>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5392496>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5392498>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5392500>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5392504> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5392494>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2: Diplothyrus lecorrei n. sp. Larva, gnathosoma. (a) – chelicera; (b) – palp, anterolateral view; (c) – palp tarsus, detail, anterolat- eral view; (d) – subcapitulum. Scale for a, b, d identical, scale bar = 100 µm; scale bar for c = 50 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5392494/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5392496>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3: Diplothyrus lecorrei n. sp. Larva, idiosoma, reconstructed. (a) – dorsal view; (b) – ventral view. Scale bar = 100 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5392496/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5392498>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4: Diplothyrus lecorrei n. sp. Larva, legs. (a) – leg I; (b) – detail tarsus I; (c) – leg II; (d) – leg III. Scale bar for a, c, d = 100 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5392498/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5392500>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5: Diplothyrus lecorrei n. sp. Female. (a) – chelicera (details of whole chelicera and membranous outgrowth); (b) – palp, anterolateral (left) and posterolateral (right) views (setae drawn in dashed lines not consistently present); (c) – subcapitulum; (d) – genital area (arrow indicates presumed latigynal shield), open circles: setal bases, filled grey circles: pores; (e) – pretarsus II. Scale bars = 200 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5392500/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5392504>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6: Diplothyrus lecorrei n. sp. Adult, idiosoma. (a) – male, ventral view; (b) – female, ventral view; (c) – male, Thon’s organ; (d) – female, Thon’s organ, detail view. Scale bars for a, b = 500 µm; scale bars for c, d = 200 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5392504/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

